\nCausal tokens: 0\r\nAvg CFI of scaffolding: 0.975\r\nAvg CFI of causal: 0.000"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2585,"aggregated":"=== CONDITIONAL IMPORTANCE ANALYSIS ===\r\nDelta < 0 means removing token HURTS prediction (token is causal)\r\nDelta ~ 0 means removing token doesn't matter (token is scaffolding)\r\n\r\nToken                          Freq    CFI   Jac+Tok  Jac-Tok    Delta\r\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\nfor next instantiation           199  1.000   0.3845   0.3839  -0.0006\r\ncompleted at:                    199  1.000   0.3845   0.3839  -0.0006\r\ninstantiation -                  199  1.000   0.3845   0.3839  -0.0006\r\n## for                           199  1.000   0.3845   0.3839  -0.0006\r\n## for next                      199  1.000   0.3845   0.3839  -0.0006\r\nfor next                         199  1.000   0.3845   0.3839  -0.0006\r\nnext instantiation               199  1.000   0.3845   0.3839  -0.0006\r\nnext instantiation -             199  1.000   0.3845   0.3839  -0.0006\r\nproposed mutations waiting:      153  1.000   0.2337   0.2331  -0.0006\r\nmutations waiting:               153  1.000   0.2337   0.2331  -0.0006\r\nproposed mutations               153  1.000   0.2337   0.2331  -0.0006\r\nllm response                     153  1.000   0.2337   0.2331  -0.0006\r\n## llm response                  153  1.000   0.2337   0.2331  -0.0006\r\n## applied mutations             153  1.000   0.2337   0.2331  -0.0006\r\n## applied                       153  1.000   0.2337   0.2331  -0.0006\r\n- proposed                       153  1.000   0.2337   0.2331  -0.0006\r\n- proposed mutations             153  1.000   0.2337   0.2331  -0.0006\r\napplied mutations                153  1.000   0.2337   0.2331  -0.0006\r\n## llm                           153  1.000   0.2337   0.2331  -0.0006\r\n- completed at:                  152  1.000   0.2348   0.2343  -0.0006\r\n- completed   